org.bukkit.material

クラス Door

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.bukkit.material.MaterialData
      • org.bukkit.material.Door
  • すべての実装されたインタフェース:
    Cloneable, Directional, Openable

    public class Door
extends MaterialData
implements Directional, Openable
    Represents a door. This class was previously deprecated, but has been retrofitted to work with modern doors. Some methods are undefined dependant on isTopHalf() due to Minecraft's internal representation of doors.
    関連項目:
    Material.WOODEN_DOOR, Material.IRON_DOOR_BLOCK, Material.SPRUCE_DOOR, Material.BIRCH_DOOR, Material.JUNGLE_DOOR, Material.ACACIA_DOOR, Material.DARK_OAK_DOOR

      • Door

        public Door(Material type,
            BlockFace face)
        Constructs the bottom half of a door of the given material type, facing the specified direction and set to closed
        パラメータ:
        type - The type of material this door is made of. This must match the type of the block above.
        face - The direction the door is facing.
        関連項目:
        Material.WOODEN_DOOR, Material.IRON_DOOR_BLOCK, Material.SPRUCE_DOOR, Material.BIRCH_DOOR, Material.JUNGLE_DOOR, Material.ACACIA_DOOR, Material.DARK_OAK_DOOR, BlockFace.WEST, BlockFace.NORTH, BlockFace.EAST, BlockFace.SOUTH

      • Door

            BlockFace face,
            boolean isOpen)
        Constructs the bottom half of a door of the given material type, facing the specified direction and set to open or closed
        パラメータ:
        type - The type of material this door is made of. This must match the type of the block above.
        face - The direction the door is facing.
        isOpen - Whether the door is currently opened.
        関連項目:
        Material.WOODEN_DOOR, Material.IRON_DOOR_BLOCK, Material.SPRUCE_DOOR, Material.BIRCH_DOOR, Material.JUNGLE_DOOR, Material.ACACIA_DOOR, Material.DARK_OAK_DOOR, BlockFace.WEST, BlockFace.NORTH, BlockFace.EAST, BlockFace.SOUTH

      • Door

        public Door(Material type,
            boolean isHingeRight)
        Constructs the top half of door of the given material type and with the hinge on the left or right
        パラメータ:
        type - The type of material this door is made of. This must match the type of the block below.
        isHingeRight - True if the hinge is on the right hand side, false if the hinge is on the left hand side.
        関連項目:
        Material.WOODEN_DOOR, Material.IRON_DOOR_BLOCK, Material.SPRUCE_DOOR, Material.BIRCH_DOOR, Material.JUNGLE_DOOR, Material.ACACIA_DOOR, Material.DARK_OAK_DOOR
